=head1 DESCRIPTION

Specifies how does the rule-based matching process should match
profiles. You can choose from the following attributes to build the
matching Rule:

=over

=item *

AccountNumber

=item *

Address.Address

=item *

Address.City

=item *

Address.Country

=item *

Address.County

=item *

Address.PostalCode

=item *

Address.State

=item *

Address.Province

=item *

BirthDate

=item *

BusinessName

=item *

EmailAddress

=item *

FirstName

=item *

Gender

=item *

LastName

=item *

MiddleName

=item *

PhoneNumber

=item *

Any customized profile attributes that start with the C<Attributes>

=back


=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Rule => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

A single rule level of the C<MatchRules>. Configures how the rule-based
matching process should match profiles.



